OL,6,FA baby boy who has been in hospital
OL,7,Ffor the majority of his life is
OL,8,Fpreparing to spend his first Christmas
OL,9,Fat home after finally being discharged.
OL,11,FBertie Melly weighed just 1lb 10oz
OL,12,Fwhen he was born prematurely at 24
OL,13,Fweeks in May 2024.
OL,15,FHe has undergone five operations in
OL,16,Fhis short life after being diagnosed
OL,17,Fwith a potentially life-threatening
OL,18,Fillness affecting his intestines.
