OL,3,CBaby boy who has spent the majority of
OL,4,Chis life in hospital home for Christmas
OL,6,FAfter more than 500 days in hospital
OL,7,FBertie is now at home with his
OL,8,Fparents, Phoebe and Callum Melly, who
OL,9,Fdescribe their son as a "remarkable
OL,10,Flittle human being".
OL,12,FThe family, from Bromley, is planning
OL,13,Fto spend time with their loved ones
OL,14,Fover Christmas.
