OL,3,CBaby boy who has spent the majority of
OL,4,Chis life in hospital home for Christmas
OL,6,FBertie was born after a 17-minute
OL,7,Flabour at St Thomas' Hospital in
OL,8,FLondon and was diagnosed with
OL,9,Fnecrotising enterocolitis, a serious
OL,10,Fcondition which causes tissue in the
OL,11,Fintestines to become inflamed and
OL,12,Fstart to die.
OL,14,FHe had his first surgery on his bowel
OL,15,Fat 10 days old.
