OL,3,CBaby boy who has spent the majority of
OL,4,Chis life in hospital home for Christmas
OL,6,FBertie spent the first six months of
OL,7,Fhis life in neonatal intensive care
OL,8,Fbefore being moved to Evelina London
OL,9,FChildren's Hospital, with his parents
OL,10,Fstaying at the nearby Ronald McDonald
OL,11,FHouse.
OL,13,FMr Melly, 37, told the Press
OL,14,FAssociation that Bertie is the
OL,15,F"happiest child you will ever meet".
