OL,3,CBaby boy who has spent the majority of
OL,4,Chis life in hospital home for Christmas
OL,6,FHe said: "Considering everything he's
OL,7,Fbeen through ` if you see his hands,
OL,8,Fhis hands are covered in scars from
OL,9,Fthe amount of cannulas he's had, he's
OL,10,Fgot gaping scars all over his his
OL,11,Fabdomen ` and he wakes up beaming,
OL,12,Fgoes to bed, beaming.
OL,14,F"He's a remarkable little human being."
OL,16,FMrs Melly, 34, puts her son's
OL,17,Fcharacter down to the "love and
OL,18,Faffection" he received from doctors
OL,19,Fand nurses.
