OL,3,CBaby boy who has spent the majority of
OL,4,Chis life in hospital home for Christmas
OL,6,FShe told PA: "In the NICU and in the
OL,7,Fpaediatric ward at the Evelina,
OL,8,Feveryone just loved him and genuinely
OL,9,Freally cared for him, which was so
OL,10,Fnice, and I think that's really helped
OL,11,Fhim to get to where he is today."
OL,13,FBertie was allowed home in November
OL,14,Fafter 547 days in hospital.
OL,16,FAccording to the Evelina's neonatal
OL,17,Fteam, the average length of time spent
OL,18,Fin NICU for a baby born at 24 weeks is
OL,19,Faround six months.
