OL,3,CBaby boy who has spent the majority of
OL,4,Chis life in hospital home for Christmas
OL,6,FMrs Melly told PA her son is
OL,7,F"thriving" since coming home.
OL,9,FShe added: "He's physically developing
OL,10,Freally well, I think he's not that far
OL,11,Foff walking now.
OL,13,F"He's climbing up the stairs, on and
OL,14,Foff the sofa, and getting a bit more
OL,15,Fconfident with his standing."
OL,17,FMr Melly said: "We've only been home
OL,18,Ffor four weeks, but it's almost a
OL,19,Fdistant memory now being at the
OL,20,Fhospital, which is really nice, just
OL,21,Fso normal."
