OL,6,FThe couple have taken Bertie to see
OL,7,FFather Christmas, although Mrs Melly
OL,8,Fsaid he was "more interested in all
OL,9,Fthe decorations".
OL,11,FShe is looking forward to buying her
OL,12,Fson presents this year as the family
OL,13,Fwere limited on space at the hospital.
OL,15,FMrs Melly also told PA her son is
OL,16,F"making some really good progress"
OL,17,Fmedically.
