OL,3,CBaby boy who has spent the majority of
OL,4,Chis life in hospital home for Christmas
OL,6,FShe said that while "there is always a
OL,7,Frisk that he could get a bowel
OL,8,Fobstruction" later in life, it is not
OL,9,Fa certainty.
OL,11,FFollowing his operations, Bertie has
OL,12,Fwhat is known as a short gut, as he
OL,13,Flost around 70% of his small intestine.
OL,15,FHe has also been tube-fed milk and has
OL,16,Fan IV line that gives him vitamins,
OL,17,Fminerals and amino acids straight into
OL,18,Fhis bloodstream.
