OL,6,FHowever, the family's goal is to now
OL,7,Fup the amount of solids the toddler is
OL,8,Feating so he can be eventually weaned
OL,9,Foff both lines.
OL,11,FMr Melly said he is hopeful his son
OL,12,Fcan have the IV nutrition line ` which
OL,13,Fgoes straight to Bertie's heart `
OL,14,Fremoved in six months to a year.
OL,16,FHe told PA: "If he can get that line
OL,17,Fout, then it means we can have a
OL,18,Fpretty much normal life until he's
OL,19,Feating enough to get the milk pump
OL,20,Fremoved as well."
