OL,6,FMrs Melly said she was initially "very
OL,7,Frelaxed" when she went to hospital in
OL,8,FMay 2024 after experiencing some
OL,9,Fbleeding, as an assessment deemed her
OL,10,Fat low risk of actually giving birth.
OL,12,FShe was told she may need to stay in
OL,13,Ffor a week for bed rest and then would
OL,14,Fbe sent home for the remainder of her
OL,15,Fpregnancy.
OL,17,F"We didn't know what was ahead, and I
OL,18,Factually think that was probably a
OL,19,Fgood thing, because we literally just
OL,20,Ftook each day as it came," she said.
