OL,3,CBaby boy who has spent the majority of
OL,4,Chis life in hospital home for Christmas
OL,6,F"We didn't think too far ahead. We
OL,7,Ftackled one problem at a time."
OL,9,FMrs Melly said Bertie's "biggest"
OL,10,Fhealth issue at birth was his bowel,
OL,11,Fbut the family also "went through a
OL,12,Flot" with his breathing.
OL,14,F"He was intubated for a long time, and
OL,15,Fthere was times when his lungs were
OL,16,Ffully about to give up," she added.
OL,18,F"You just can't think too far ahead `
OL,19,Fthere were times I wouldn't have even
OL,20,Fthought we'd be sat here today, and
OL,21,Fwe're at home with him.
