OL,3,CBaby boy who has spent the majority of
OL,4,Chis life in hospital home for Christmas
OL,6,F"So in that sense, it's comforting to
OL,7,Fknow that, although you've got those
OL,8,Fdark fears, actually, we've made so
OL,9,Fmuch progress in 18 months, so who
OL,10,Fknows where we'll be in a year's time
OL,11,Fas well."
OL,13,FThe couple said they are "eternally
OL,14,Fgrateful" to the team at the Evelina
OL,15,Ffor everything they did for Bertie.
OL,17,FMr Melly added: "They saved his life
OL,18,Fat the end of the day, on countless
OL,19,Foccasions."
