OL,6,FIain Yardley, consultant paediatric
OL,7,Fand neonatal surgeon at Evelina
OL,8,FLondon, who was involved in Bertie's
OL,9,Fcare, said: "Bertie has faced many,
OL,10,Fmany challenges in his short life.
OL,12,F"He and his parents have faced these
OL,13,Fchallenges with extraordinary grace
OL,14,Fand courage.
OL,16,F"Seeing him go home is what we all
OL,17,Fhave been working for and we could not
OL,18,Fbe more pleased for him and his
OL,19,Ffamily."
